title: Thambikku Entha Ooru
subTitle: Seeing Balu's spendthrift and carefree attitude, his father sends him to his friend's house in a village to get reformed. Things get complicated when he gets entangled in a love triangle.

title: Mr. Bharath
subTitle: A businessman abandons his first love, to marry a rich heiress. However, things take a turn when his illegitimate son seeks revenge for the injustice done to his mother.

title: Gentleman
subTitle: Kicha is a modern-day Robin Hood, who along with his friend, Mani, steals from the rich to aid the poor. In society, he is a respected man who runs a small business.

title: Billa
subTitle: When Billa, a don, dies at the hands of ACP Murthy, he is replaced by Ranga, his lookalike, to infiltrate the gang. When Murthy is killed, Ranga is trapped since only Murthy knew the truth.

title: Kaalam Maari Pochu
subTitle: Indra and her three sisters are married off to mediocre men by their patriarchal father. However, he realises their importance when his son stirs discord in the family.

title: Nayagan
subTitle: A man who witnesses the gruesome murder of his father kills a corrupt policeman and flees to Mumbai to become a gangster.

title: Thooral Ninnu Pochu
subTitle: Two families arrange the marriage of their son and daughter, who fall in love. However, tensions arise when the families clash over dowry demands, leading to the cancellation of the wedding.

title: Vanaja Girija
subTitle: Sisters Vanaja and Girija believe they were abandoned by their father due to the influence of a man named Ramanathan. The duo vow to alienate Ramanathan from his family as he did to theirs.

title: Veettukku Veedu Vasappadi
subTitle: Jagan, a successful doctor, ties the knot with Jaya. However, their marital life becomes increasingly strained due to Jagan's profession.
